org.epochx.stats
Class StatField

java.lang.Object
  org.epochx.stats.StatField
Direct Known Subclasses:
GEStatField, GPStatField, GRStatField
public class StatField
extends java.lang.Object

Provides constants to be used as keys to request statistics from the StatsManager.

RUN_NUMBER

public static final java.lang.String RUN_NUMBER
Returns an Integer which is the sequential identifier of the last run in the series of runs. The first run will be run number 0.

See Also:

RUN_FITNESS_MIN

public static final java.lang.String RUN_FITNESS_MIN
Returns a Double which is the lowest fitness score achieved by a CandidateProgram in the last run. Note that standardised fitness is used, so the best program has the minimum fitness.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

GEN_FITNESSES

public static final java.lang.String GEN_FITNESSES
Returns a double[] which contains the fitnesses of all the CandidatePrograms in the population at the end of the previous generation. The fitnesses are arbitrarily ordered.
